1. It is a best practice when setting up a Linux System to create each Directory into a Single Partiton. Now with Windows and Google, you may have to recreate your Linux with a Partition Tool 
/boot 5-10 MB
/ 256 MB
/usr 512MB
/home 5700MB
/var 256 MB
/tmp 333MB
Swap 512MB
/chroot 256 MB
/var/lib 1000MB
üö® By Setting your Directories in a Separate partion, this stops and defends against DOS Attacks.
